    "body": "So these are the steps I took.\r\n\r\n1. git cloned https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse.git\r\n2. Built docker image from source(lighthouse:local)\r\n3. Modified your Git docker-compose file to reference local lighthouse image and executed docker-compose up in the lighthouse-docker directory\r\n - Initially ran on Either Friday or Saturday 26th/27th June for the first time and stopped the docker container a few mins after\r\n4. Executed again(in same directory) on Sunday/Monday and got the error reported. (I might have recompiled from source again)\r\n\r\nif I compiled from source on Friday would that have been a Witti node? I did use the same directory when executing\r\n\r\nThanks",
